    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Need a gas safety certificate on the Wirral today?</h3>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Same-day CP12 inspections available across all Wirral CH postcodes. £80 fixed price. No call-out fee. Certificate emailed same day.</p>
      <a href="tel:0151 558 0334" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg" style="box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(249,115,22,0.4);color:#ffffff;">CALL 0151 558 0334</a>
    </div>
