  <!-- WHAT IF FAULT FOUND -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:#f8fafc;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Happens If the Inspection Finds a Problem?</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub">We follow the Gas Industry Unsafe Situations Procedure on every Wirral inspection.</p>
      <div class="pf-who-grid" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <div class="pf-who-item" style="border-left:3px solid #dc2626;">
          <div style="background:#dc2626;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1rem;min-width:1.75rem;height:1.75rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">1</div>
          <div><strong>Immediately Dangerous</strong><p>If an appliance poses an immediate risk, our engineer turns it off, disconnects the gas supply and places a warning notice. We explain and provide a written repair quote. A CP12 cannot be issued until the fault is rectified.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-who-item" style="border-left:3px solid #d97706;">
          <div style="background:#d97706;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1rem;min-width:1.75rem;height:1.75rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">2</div>
          <div><strong>At Risk</strong><p>If an appliance has a fault that could become dangerous but is not immediately so, we advise and provide a written repair quote. We strongly recommend addressing At Risk faults before the next tenancy. A CP12 can be issued noting the fault.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-who-item" style="border-left:3px solid #16a34a;">
          <div style="background:#16a34a;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1rem;min-width:1.75rem;height:1.75rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">3</div>
          <div><strong>Not to Current Standard</strong><p>Older appliances that meet the standard at installation but not current standards. Noted on the CP12 with a recommendation. The appliance passes but the issue is documented.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes">
          <span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span>
          <div><strong>Written quote before any repair work</strong><p>If a repair is needed, we provide a written quote before any additional work starts. We never begin repair work without your approval. Straightforward repairs can often be completed on the same visit.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- WIRRAL HMO SECTION -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:#f1f5f9;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Wirral HMO Landlords and Gas Safety</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub">The Wirral has a significant and growing HMO sector, concentrated in Birkenhead CH41, Wallasey CH44 and Bebington CH63. Gas safety compliance is a mandatory condition of every HMO licence.</p>
